name: "Idiot Shooter"
description: Mick we spend most of our time watching action movies. his routine life started to get boring as time passed. He was bored of watching his favorite movies and wanted to put into practice. One day, while wandering around the Junkland ghettos, he stumbled upon an old gun. wiped the gun with a cloth soaked in machine oil and polished it. He started shooting, not caring whether there was a bullet or not, and then BANG BANG!
